<h2>Protocol: For Each</h2><p>Iterates over a collection (Array, Observable, or Promise) and stamps a template for each item.</p><h3>Virtual Implementation</h3><p>Uses Custom Comments (e.g. <code>&lt;!-- control:for-each --&gt;</code>) to mark the list boundaries. This behaves like a Repeater without a wrapper element.</p><h3>Usage Example</h3><pre><code class="language-html">&lt;!-- control:for-each 
  items="users" 
  key="id" 
--&gt;
  &lt;template&gt;
    &lt;div class="user-row"&gt;
       &lt;span data-bind="name"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/template&gt;
&lt;!-- /control:for-each --&gt;</code></pre>